{"tid":1251223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都有讀過書","createTime":"2019-06-22T12:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T13:37:11.000Z","uid":137789,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc84094262dad30ba7556e119ab75391c16dafa","tid":1251223,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺自己讀書嘅年代，學校就係一個社會嘅縮影，身邊好多唔同嘅人，有啲係垃圾人，冇腦，成日做啲戇鳩嘢，暴力，鐘意結黨，呢啲人好多讀唔成書，又有啲陰陰濕濕嘅人，唔會同人正面衝突，一有機會就喺人背後插一刀，呢啲人好多時都讀到下書。好多時我哋都唔會理呢啲人。<br />\n<br />\n很後多年後，個個出晒社會，啲讀唔成書嗰班就做晒毅進仔，陰陰濕濕嗰班就考督察，靠陰陰濕濕爬到上高位，喺毅進仔上面指手劃腳，然後我哋就要面對返佢哋。"},{"pid":"64a6a080fc6763fe9438e156c721a2aac3fcbe30","tid":1251223,"uid":227788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"你當年有冇怕佢地? <br />\n如果冇 而家都唔使怕!"},{"pid":"19a7e4bfc7cbe032bc560661e37c98a5271b7236","tid":1251223,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"好想呢班人死"},{"pid":"b142b369f4a5c76e28199b6053ebf0ed46e752be","tid":1251223,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4abff749ef963055d20c0b4c559b17d9f1908f9","tid":1251223,"uid":137789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b142b369f4a5c76e28199b6053ebf0ed46e752be","tid":1251223,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a7e4bfc7cbe032bc560661e37c98a5271b7236","tid":1251223,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"好想呢班人死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"唔死都冇用"},{"pid":"afc317d9397c9dbf385f1858c86161eacdd55fb3","tid":1251223,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"636c89b603a0ee490f16cc5658f955d1f8b4f1fc","tid":1251223,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afc317d9397c9dbf385f1858c86161ea